<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212438>
    bibo:endPage "64" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "52" ;
    bibo:volume "3391" ;
    dc:creator "Dehling, Maximilian" ;
    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "An African glass frog: A new Hyperolius species (Anura: Hyperoliidae) from Nyungwe National Park, southern Rwanda" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212439>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212440>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212441>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212442> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212439>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Holotype of Hyperolius jackie sp. n. in life (ZMB 77476). Photograph taken in situ." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212439/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212440>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dorsal view (A) and ventral view (B) of five type specimens of Hyperolius jackie sp. n. Top row from left to right: ZMB 77477 – 77479 (paratypes), bottom row from left to right: ZMB 77476 (holotype), 77480 (paratype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212440/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212441>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. (A) Audiospectrogram and (B) oscillogram of a call series of the holotype of Hyperolius jackie sp. n. (ZMB 77476), including an initial note (call type 2) followed by three advertisement calls. (C) Oscillogram of a single advertisement call." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212441/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212442>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Recording sites of Hyperolius jackie sp. n. in Nyungwe National Park, southern Rwanda. Red star: Type locality at Karamba. Yellow star: Second locality at stream near the forest edge." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212442/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

